animals.name: Lion
animals.characteristics: Large mane in males, powerful build, social behavior.
animals.description: Known as the king of the jungle, lions live in prides and are apex predators.

animals.name: Bengal Tiger
animals.characteristics: Orange fur with black stripes, excellent swimmer.
animals.description: Largest of all wild cats, known for their distinctive stripes and solitary nature.

animals.name: Giant Panda
animals.characteristics: Black and white coloring, specialized bamboo diet.
animals.description: Beloved bear species that primarily feeds on bamboo and is a symbol of conservation.

animals.name: Arctic Wolf
animals.characteristics: White fur, thick coat, pack hunter.
animals.description: Adapted to life in the Arctic, these wolves hunt in packs and have excellent survival skills.

animals.name: Emperor Penguin
animals.description: Known for their remarkable parenting behaviors in extreme conditions.

animals.name: Komodo Dragon
animals.characteristics: Largest living lizard, powerful bite, venomous.
animals.description: Ancient species of monitor lizard known for their size and hunting abilities.

animals.name: Red Kangaroo
animals.description: Largest marsupial, known for carrying young in pouches.

animals.name: Blue Whale
animals.description: The largest animal known to have existed, feeding primarily on krill.

animals.name: African Elephant
animals.description: Largest land animal, known for their intelligence and complex social structures.

animals.name: Great White Shark
animals.characteristics: Powerful predator, excellent sense of smell.
animals.description: Apex predator of the oceans, known for their size and hunting abilities.

comments.text: Has anyone seen Kung Fu Panda? :)
